msgid "AitAttman Blocks"
msgstr "AitAttman Blocks"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: aitattman-blocks.php
msgid "https://github.com/AitAttman/aitattman-blocks"
msgstr "https://github.com/AitAttman/aitattman-blocks"

#. Description of the plugin
#: aitattman-blocks.php
msgid "Enable Wordpress custom blocks like Side-panel, Search Box, Query Posts, Button, Slider and Theme Controllers"
msgstr "Activez des blocs personnalisés WordPress tels que le Panneau latéral, la Boîte de recherche, la Requête d'articles, le Bouton, le Curseur et les Contrôleurs de thème."

#. Author of the plugin
